  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is hypothesized that, when given at the lowest effective dose, the favorable side effect
      profile combined with it's lower propensity for weight gain would make SPN-810 a candidate
      for treatment of persistent serious conduct problems in pediatric subjects with ADHD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
